Interface GenericDAO<T,K>

Type Parameters:
T - the entity type managed by the DAO
K - the type of the entity identifier (e.g., Long, String, UUID)
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractGenericDAO, BiomedicalEquipmentDAO, EntryRequestDAO, EquipmentDAO, PersonDAO, ProviderDAO, TechEquipmentDAO
public interface GenericDAO<T,K>
Generic DAO interface that defines the basic CRUD operations to be implemented by concrete data-access classes.

This interface abstracts the fundamental persistence operations for any entity type, enabling reusable and type-safe data handling across the application.
